high_descs: Head towards the door ahead and walk to the sink on the right.
Open the lower left cabinet under the sink, pick up the bar of soap on the right and close the door.
Look up at the sink of the vanity.
Put the bar of soap inside the left sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the tub on the left.
Put the rinsed bar of soap inside the tub in the middle area.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap inside a tub.

high_descs: Take two steps forward then turn right and walk to the sink.
Open the cabinet under the sink to your left and get the bar of pink soap that's on the right.
Get the bar of soap wet in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and take a step then turn left and walk to the tub.
Put the bar of soap in the tub near the wall that you're near.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap in the tub.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the sink.
Open the bottom left cabinet and take out a bar of soap.
Hold the bar of soap and look up.
Place the bar of soap in the sink and turn on the water. Turn of the water and pick up the soap.
Carry the soap and turn to the right to find the bath tub.
Place the soap inside the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a bar of soap and place it in the bath tub.
